---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy | RangeDOPE" description="RangeDOPE privacy policy — your data never leaves your device.">
<style>
  nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 clamp(20px,5vw,60px);height:80px;background:rgba(8,8,8,0.9);backdrop-filter:blur(16px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .brand{font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:20px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.15em;color:#fff;font-style:italic;}
  .brand span{color:var(--primary);}
  main{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:140px clamp(20px,5vw,40px) 100px;}
  .back{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;color:var(--dim);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:48px;}
  .back:hover{color:var(--primary);opacity:1;}
  .spec-tag{display:inline-block;background:var(--primary);color:#fff;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.2em;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 10px;margin-bottom:20px;}
  h1{font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:clamp(36px,6vw,56px);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.02em;color:#fff;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:28px;}
  .meta{display:flex;gap:40px;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;margin-bottom:0;padding-bottom:40px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .meta-item{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;}
  .meta-key{color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:9px;}
  .meta-val{color:var(--primary);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.05em;}
  section{margin-top:48px;}
  h2{font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:#fff;text-transform:uppercase;border-left:4px solid var(--primary);padding-left:16px;margin-bottom:16px;}
  p{font-size:16px;color:#888;line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:16px;}
  .tech-tag{display:inline-block;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:2px 7px;border:1px solid rgba(255,48,0,.4);background:rgba(255,48,0,.08);color:var(--primary);vertical-align:middle;margin:0 3px;}
  ul.data-list{list-style:none;border:1px solid var(--border);background:rgba(18,18,18,.5);padding:24px 28px;margin:16px 0;}
  ul.data-list li{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;font-size:14px;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.6;}
  ul.data-list li:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
  ul.data-list li::before{content:'◆';color:var(--primary);font-size:9px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:4px;}
  .notice-box{border-left:4px solid var(--primary);background:var(--surface);padding:24px 28px;margin:20px 0;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
  .notice-label{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:#fff;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .notice-box p{font-size:13px;font-family:var(--font-mono);color:#888;margin-bottom:0;}
  .partners{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;margin-top:16px;}
  .partner{border:1px solid var(--border);padding:20px;}
  .partner-cat{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.2em;color:var(--primary);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .partner-name{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .partner p{font-size:12px;color:var(--dim);margin-bottom:0;}
  .contact-box{margin-top:80px;padding-top:40px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;background:var(--surface);padding:32px;border:1px solid var(--border);}
  .contact-box h3{font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .contact-box p{margin-bottom:0;}
  .btn-contact{display:inline-block;background:#fff;color:#000;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.2em;padding:14px 32px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;}
  .btn-contact:hover{background:var(--primary);color:#fff;opacity:1;}
  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:32px clamp(20px,5vw,60px);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;}
  footer a{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.18em;color:var(--dim);text-transform:uppercase;}
  footer a:hover{color:var(--primary);opacity:1;}
  footer span{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--dim2);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;}
  @media(max-width:600px){.partners{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.meta{flex-wrap:wrap;gap:24px;}}
</style>

<nav>
  <a href="/" style="opacity:1;text-decoration:none;"><span class="brand">RANGE<span>DOPE</span></span></a>
</nav>

<main>
  <a href="/" class="back">← Back to Home</a>

  <div class="spec-tag">Legal Specification</div>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <div class="meta">
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-key">Effective Date</span><span class="meta-val">2026.01.12</span></div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-key">Last Updated</span><span class="meta-val">2026.05.03</span></div>
    <div class="meta-item"><span class="meta-key">System Version</span><span class="meta-val" style="color:#fff;">v1.1.0-BETA</span></div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <h2>01. Overview</h2>
    <p>At RangeDOPE, we prioritize operational security. This Privacy Policy describes how your information is handled when you use the RangeDOPE Precision Ballistics System. We operate under a <span class="tech-tag">ZERO-RETENTION</span> default — your data stays on your device.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>02. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>To provide precision ballistic calculations, the application accesses specific device capabilities. This includes GPS coordinates <span class="tech-tag">WHEN IN USE ONLY</span>, local atmospheric sensors, and device orientation. Nothing is transmitted to our servers.</p>
    <ul class="data-list">
      <li><strong>Atmospheric Data:</strong> Barometric pressure, humidity, and temperature — used locally for ballistic solutions only.</li>
      <li><strong>GPS / Location:</strong> Used to fill Shooter coordinates in Shot Plan mode. Only accessed when you tap GPS. Never stored remotely.</li>
      <li><strong>Ballistic Profiles:</strong> Rifle, load, and scope configurations stored locally on your device in SQLite.</li>
      <li><strong>Subscription Status:</strong> Managed via <span class="tech-tag">REVENUECAT</span> to verify active Pro license. RevenueCat receives a hashed device ID and transaction receipts only.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>03. Data Security</h2>
    <p>All ballistic profiles and hunt data are stored locally. We do not transmit your location, firing positions, or hunt logs to any server. Your data is never sold, shared, or monetized.</p>
    <div class="notice-box">
      <div class="notice-label">Critical Notice</div>
      <p>Deleting the application results in permanent removal of all locally stored ballistic profiles and waypoints. Use the Export feature before uninstalling to preserve your data.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>04. Third-Party Integrations</h2>
    <p>We use a minimal set of technical partners to ensure system stability and payment processing.</p>
    <div class="partners">
      <div class="partner">
        <div class="partner-cat">Crash Reporting</div>
        <div class="partner-name">Sentry</div>
        <p>Anonymous crash and error reporting. No user-identifiable data. Helps us fix bugs fast.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="partner">
        <div class="partner-cat">Billing</div>
        <div class="partner-name">RevenueCat + App Store</div>
        <p>In-app purchase verification via Apple StoreKit. We never see your payment details.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="partner">
        <div class="partner-cat">Weather</div>
        <div class="partner-name">Open-Meteo</div>
        <p>Free, anonymous weather API. Your location is sent only to fetch wind data; it is not stored.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="partner">
        <div class="partner-cat">Mapping</div>
        <div class="partner-name">USGS / ESRI / BLM</div>
        <p>Free government tile servers. Tile requests are standard HTTP — no user tracking.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>05. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Because we collect no personal data on our servers, there is nothing to request deletion of. All your data lives on your iPhone. Delete the app to remove everything. You can also export your profiles at any time from the Settings tab.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>06. Contact</h2>
    <div class="contact-box">
      <div>
        <h3>Legal Support</h3>
        <p>For inquiries regarding data privacy or requests for information.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <a href="mailto:mike@techridgeseo.com" class="btn-contact">CONTACT_OPS</a>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--dim2);letter-spacing:.15em;text-align:center;margin-top:10px;text-transform:uppercase;">Response within 24–48H</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:24px;">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/privacy" style="color:#fff;">Privacy Policy</a>
    <a href="mailto:mike@techridgeseo.com">Support</a>
  </div>
  <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} RangeDOPE. All rights reserved.</span>
</footer>

</Base>
